title: Deadline (01 - 04) (2002)
description:
Deadline (01 - 04) (2002) 


Daily Bugle reporter Kate Ferral is introduced in this four-issue limited series, as she must interact with the Marvel Universe's heroes and villains in order to stop the mysterious Judge from killing again. Notable appearances by the Tinkerer, the New York franchise of the Bar With No Name, and the almost completely insignificant death of the equally unimportant Carjack.
